<!-- SECTION 2B: WEALTH STRATEGY ASSESSMENT QUIZ -->
<!-- =========================================== -->
<div class="section" id="s02b">
  <div class="section-label">02b / The Wealth Strategy Assessment</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">The Quiz That Qualifies Your Leads</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">A multi-step assessment tool that scores digital asset readiness and delivers personalised result tiers. Not a generic quiz. Every question is designed to qualify the lead AND give them genuine value. The result page is personalised based on their answers, making it feel like a real diagnostic - not a lead gen trap. Collects name, email, phone, and budget range.</p>

  <!-- What the quiz IS -->
  <div class="card" style="border-top:3px solid var(--orange);">
    <div class="card-title">How It Works</div>
    <div class="stats-bar">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Questions</div>
        <div class="stat-value">5</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Time</div>
        <div class="stat-value white">3 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Form Fields</div>
        <div class="stat-value white">4</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Result Tiers</div>
        <div class="stat-value">3</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Destination</div>
        <div class="stat-value green">Setter Call</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout">
      <strong>The mechanism:</strong> 5 strategic questions → personalised result page with dynamic headline, portfolio-specific summary, insight cards, and risk profile → CTA to book a strategy session. The lead feels assessed, not pitched. Every answer shapes the output, so no two results look the same.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Question Flow -->
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px;">
    <div class="card-title">Question Flow</div>

    <div class="flow">
      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--orange);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--orange);">Q1 - Wealth Goal</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"What is your primary financial goal right now?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          &#127963;&#65039; Building generational wealth &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128200; Growing portfolio faster &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#9200; Financial independence &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128737;&#65039; Protecting from inflation
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&#8595;</div>

      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--green);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--green);">Q2 - Current Portfolio</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"How would you describe your current investment portfolio?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          &#127968; Heavily property &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128202; Primarily equities/super &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#9878;&#65039; Balanced mix &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#127970; Mostly business equity
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&#8595;</div>

      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--purple);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--purple);">Q3 - Biggest Barrier</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"What do you feel is the biggest thing keeping you from reaching your current wealth goals?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          &#128201; Inflation eroding savings &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128202; Stock market unpredictability &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128506;&#65039; No clear growth strategy &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#9200; Retirement timeline pressure
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--orange);margin-top:6px;">&#8594; Skip link available: "Already know digital assets are right for me → Skip to get my blueprint"</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&#8595;</div>

      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--blue);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--blue);">Q4 - Digital Asset Familiarity</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"Have you considered looking into digital assets as a hedge yet?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          &#127793; Haven't explored yet &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#129300; Heard but skeptical &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128269; Looked into it, no move &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#9989; Already started/researching
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&#8595;</div>

      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--orange);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--orange);">Q5 - Readiness to Act</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"If you had enough confidence, would you consider making this a meaningful part of your long-term portfolio?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          &#128170; Yes, absolutely &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#9878;&#65039; Possibly, depends on risk &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#128301; Open, need more info &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          &#129335; Not sure yet
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&#8595;</div>

      <div class="flow-step" style="border-left:3px solid var(--green);background:rgba(5,158,120,0.04);">
        <div class="flow-step-label" style="color:var(--green);">Form - Lead Capture</div>
        <div style="font-size:12.5px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">"One last step - where should we send your personalised blueprint?"</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">
          Fields: Full name, Email, Mobile number, Budget range (Under $10K / $10K-$50K / $50K-$250K / $250K+ / Not sure)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3 Result Tiers -->
  <div style="margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--orange);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;">Result Tiers + Follow-Up Routing</div>

  <div class="card-grid-3">
    <!-- Not Ready Yet -->
    <div class="card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--red);">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;"><span class="tag tag-red">Score &lt;40</span></div>
      <div class="card-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--red);">Not Ready Yet</div>
      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;">
        <p style="margin-bottom:8px;">Early stage. Skeptical or has not explored digital assets yet. Low readiness signals.</p>
        <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">What happens next:</div>
