          <li>Educational email sequence (5 emails over 10 days)</li>
          <li>Invite to free webinar / CWB event</li>
          <li>Add to BRIEF (weekly intelligence) nurture</li>
          <li>Re-assess readiness in 30 days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Getting Closer -->
    <div class="card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--orange);">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;"><span class="tag tag-orange">Score 40-70</span></div>
      <div class="card-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--orange);">Getting Closer</div>
      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;">
        <p style="margin-bottom:8px;">Interested but needs more conviction. Has looked into it or is actively researching. Warm lead.</p>
        <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">What happens next:</div>
        <ul class="checklist" style="font-size:11px;">
          <li>Lead magnet offer (STRATEGY or BLUEPRINT)</li>
          <li>7-day nurture email sequence</li>
          <li>Invite to strategy call (soft CTA)</li>
          <li>VSL link in follow-up DM</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Ready to Act -->
    <div class="card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--green);">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;"><span class="tag tag-green">Score 70+</span></div>
      <div class="card-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--green);">Ready to Act</div>
      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;">
        <p style="margin-bottom:8px;">High conviction. Already started or has clear intent. Budget range identified. Hot lead.</p>
        <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">What happens next:</div>
        <ul class="checklist" style="font-size:11px;">
          <li>Direct Setter call booking CTA on result page</li>
          <li>Immediate setter outreach (phone + email)</li>
          <li>Personalised blueprint emphasises speed</li>
          <li>Priority booking - fastest path to Platinum</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Traffic Integration -->
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px;">
    <div class="card-title">Traffic Source Integration</div>
    <div class="card-grid-2" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div style="padding:12px;background:var(--card-raised);border-radius:8px;border-left:3px solid var(--green);">
        <div style="font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px;">&#127793; Organic Path</div>
