  <!-- Personalisation Engine -->
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px;">
    <div class="card-title">Personalisation Engine</div>
    <p style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:12px;">The quiz generates 16 unique result combinations based on Q1 (goal) × Q2 (portfolio). Each combination gets a tailored summary explaining how digital assets fit their specific situation. Plus dynamic insight cards based on Q3 (barrier) and Q4 (familiarity), and a readiness-based CTA from Q5.</p>
